item.title: ZachSchell Post
item.description: This Markdown language is interesting. Zach Schell Start of Hugo Date: 8/21/2022 Today within Hugo we started an made the first post of content. This is all one content of a post, but the attributes can be diifrent. We have a title attribute, the date, and this body text. This is kinda cool once you get the hang of it -Zach Schell
